    <h1 class="center-text">[% l("Regulatory Information") %]</h1>
    <div class="gr-parent gr-padding-30">
        <p class="center-text">[% l("[_1] is a licensed and regulated trading platform that serves over 1,000,000 customers globally. We hold multiple licenses to comply with regulations around the world. Since 1999, weâ€™ve served our clients with a constant and unwavering commitment to integrity and reliability. We always hold ourselves to the highest ethical standards, in addition to our regulatory requirements.", website_name) %]</p>

